Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是鬼 身体真耐打
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点露出鬼那丑陋的本体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开…玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沼兰 得等到何时你才来接我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许把这颗心脏挖出丢弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能见到你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:57.00,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:57.00,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:00.37,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:00.37,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:04.88,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:04.88,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:11.18,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾いた風に抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:11.18,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎面吹着干燥的风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:17.64,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命への 真偽を覚え 刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:17.64,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂得了生命的真伪 铭刻于心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:21.06,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ただ 傍に居たいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:21.06,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 祈愿待在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:23.86,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人を愛し 人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:23.86,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱过 恨过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:27.32,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲しさは  優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:27.32,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲伤最后化作温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:32.28,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}例え光が 消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:32.28,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算陷入无尽黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:37.12,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:37.12,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍会寻觅明日希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:41.25,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃えた血の呼吸 消え寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:41.25,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃烧的血液 停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:46.38,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:46.38,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果之缘 最终转化成奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:48.42,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:48.42,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:51.01,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:51.01,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:54.01,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闇を搔き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:54.01,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拨开黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:58.47,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手を伸ばすよ どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:58.47,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伸手向前 追寻你到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:00.85,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:00.85,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.31,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか 変えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:04.31,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总有一天 命运将会转变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:09.03,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}涙の意味 無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:09.03,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要让眼泪白流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:13.74,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}螺旋のように 蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:13.74,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如螺旋一般交织骚动的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:16.24,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吠えて 交わる FATE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:16.24,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}狂吠吧 交织的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时间在这种什么蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很好的红酒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也坐一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是不亲切啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那种地方也很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝太多的话 小狐狸们会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想到连这种拐弯抹角的关怀也马上要失去 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫拐弯抹角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要和他么一起回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会觉得寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使小狐狸们还陪伴着你也会寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想我回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醉鬼说的醉话不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种对话不要对我说 跟更可爱的女孩子说去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 有你就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不可爱又任性 还很暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我跟你一起的时候最快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滨路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个会耍嘴皮子的男人啊
